'''叶口纲'''（學名：{{lang|la|Litostomatea}}）是[[纤毛虫门|纤毛虫门]][[內大核亞門|內大核亞門]]之下的一個綱<ref name="pmid19120803">{{cite journal　|vauthors=Gao S, Song W, Ma H, etal |title=Phylogeny of six genera of the subclass Haptoria (Ciliophora, Litostomatea) inferred from sequences of the gene coding for small subunit ribosomal RNA |journal=J. Eukaryot. Microbiol. |volume=55 |issue=6 |pages=562–6 |year=2008 |pmid=19120803 |doi=10.1111/j.1550-7408.2008.00360.x}}</ref>。這個綱由下列三個亞綱組成<ref>{{cite journal|last=Vďačný|first=Peter|title=Morphological and molecular phylogeny of dileptid and tracheliid ciliates: Resolution at the base of the class Litostomatea (Ciliophora, Rhynchostomatia)|journal=Eur J Protistol |date=November 2011  |pmid=21641780|doi=10.1016/j.ejop.2011.04.006|pmc=3234341|volume=47|issue=4|pages=295–313|display-authors=etal}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Gao|first=Feng|last2=Warren|first2=Alan|last3=Zhang|first3=Qianqian|last4=Gong|first4=Jun|last5=Miao|first5=Miao|last6=Sun|first6=Ping|last7=Xu|first7=Dapeng|last8=Huang|first8=Jie|last9=Yi|first9=Zhenzhen|date=2016-04-29|title=The All-Data-Based Evolutionary Hypothesis of Ciliated Protists with a Revised Classification of the Phylum Ciliophora (Eukaryota, Alveolata)|journal=Scientific Reports|language=en|volume=6|page=24874|doi=10.1038/srep24874|issn=2045-2322|pmc=4850378|pmid=27126745|bibcode=2016NatSR...624874G}}</ref>：
* Subclass [[Haptoria|Haptoria]]
* [[毛口亚纲|毛口亚纲]] [[Trichostomatia|Trichostomatia]] <small>Butschli, 1889</small>
* Subclass [[Rhynchostomatia|Rhynchostomatia]]。{{as of|2020|8|18}}，[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]仍未承認這第三個亞綱<ref name="WoRMS_292892">{{WoRMS |id=292892 |title=Litostomatea |last1=Gordon |first1=Dennis |last2=Warren |first2=Alan |last3=Kihara |first3=Terue Cristina |last4=Vandepitte |first4=Leen |date=2011-10-17 |access-date=2020-08-18 }}</ref>。

